Transcription.Text: Tarrant smiled - the idea seemed too ridiculous. Yet the questions had seemed to him to indicate that Oxenham suspected him. At one time Tarrant had felt almost sure that the C.I.D must have learned of his meetings with haines and know about the blackmail.
